#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:2
msgid "颜色检测（Color）"
msgstr "Color Inspection"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:6
msgid "基于颜色比例校验目标区域颜色特征（如带色标识、色环等）。"
msgstr ""
"Verifies the color profile of a target region (color markings, color "
"bands, and so on) using color-ratio analysis."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:10
msgid "模板编辑器中绘制对应 ROI 后，在参数面板中配置该工具的参数。"
msgstr ""
"Draw the corresponding ROI in the Template Editor, then configure the "
"tool's parameters in the parameter panel."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:12
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:-1
msgid "模板编辑器中的颜色检测元件示例"
msgstr "Example of a Color inspection component in the Template Editor"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:18
msgid "**颜色有效比例范围（Valid Color Ratio Ranges）**：配置一组或多组颜色范围及其有效比例区间，落入范围内判 OK。"
msgstr ""
"**Valid Color Ratio Ranges**: configure one or more color ranges along "
"with their OK ratio bands; the region is judged OK when the ratio falls "
"within the band."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:20
msgid "**CRM 端子颜色（自动编程）**"
msgstr "**CRM Termination Color (auto-program)**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:22
msgid ""
"除在模板编辑器中手动绘制颜色检测框外，**自动编程** 还可为 **CRM（片式元件，如片式电阻）** "
"自动放置端子颜色检测框：在自动编程配置中勾选 **CRM 端子颜色**，系统会在每个 CRM "
"元件的两个端子（焊端）处各生成一个颜色检测框，用于校验端子颜色。端子检测框的大小由参数 **端子条宽度 (本体最长边的 %)** "
"控制（取本体最长边的百分比）。端子颜色检测项与 **元件本体颜色** 相互独立，可分别启用。"
msgstr ""
"Besides drawing color-inspection boxes by hand in the template editor, "
"**auto-program** can also place termination color-inspection boxes "
"automatically for **CRM (chip components such as chip resistors)**: check"
" **CRM Termination Color** in the auto-program configuration and the "
"system generates one color-inspection box at each of the two terminations"
" (solder ends) of every CRM component to verify the termination color. "
"The size of the termination box is set by the **Termination Band Width (%"
" of longest body side)** parameter (a percentage of the body's longest "
"side). The termination color check is independent of **Component Body "
"Color** and can be enabled on its own."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/config/detection_tools/color.rst:-1
msgid "自动编程配置：勾选 CRM 端子颜色 与 端子条宽度 参数"
